1,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:48:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係睇政府定私家？<br />\n可唔可以講下啲藥點解冇用？</blockquote><br />\n日日發作就勁勁勁驚<br />\n<br />\n驚到好似行死刑<br />\n<br />\nD藥又同抑鬱症一樣<br />\n<br />\n食完無效果第二日又來<br />\n<br />\n或者持續到幾日後"},{"pid":"5f8e7c22d3a1eed62502f0d78c45d5672c563652","tid":92171,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:51:09.000Z","msg":"日日心情就好似比isis 執行死刑<br />\n<br />\n心情重重重重<br />\n<br />\n呼吸困難"},{"pid":"8f41633bc551d39078dcd4141325bd8387324de6","tid":92171,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:53:06.000Z","msg":"想自殺的決心自覺非常大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a7974dab7b4a731f8865c3710f64a4bc5047b0","tid":92171,"uid":20589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:55:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i1.kym-cdn.com/entries/icons/original/000/005/393/i-know-that-feel.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.kym-cdn.com%2Fentries%2Ficons%2Foriginal%2F000%2F005%2F393%2Fi-know-that-feel.jpg&h=dade5216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有呢個病真係好辛苦 無底深淵嚟救命<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c042631a8746c1e6791b373d23c71a9cb62418","tid":92171,"uid":17075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:55:35.000Z","msg":"想問點先叫做有焦慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都覺得自己有但又唔知咩程度先叫有"},{"pid":"fb68f019fbf0d159c529c16f657de12dd0e35709","tid":92171,"uid":75694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T11:55:42.000Z","msg":"樓主要勇敢面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7612a390dc17c544cc5739bade56ca58b8968589","tid":92171,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T12:00:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問點先叫做有焦慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都覺得自己有但又唔知咩程度先叫有</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n死刑前的心情"},{"pid":"36a28e87a4847edd64d2512accbcda0f4ce8fca9","tid":92171,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T12:09:44.000Z","msg":"你地焦慮食咩藥？"},{"pid":"629fa96bfe51f80bdcf0bcd514ec86537cf2da87","tid":92171,"uid":34701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T12:17:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主係睇政府定私家？<br />\n可唔可以講下啲藥點解冇用？</blockquote><br />\n日日發作就勁勁勁驚<br />\n<br />\n驚到好似行死刑<br />\n<br />\nD藥又同抑鬱症一樣<br />\n<br />\n食完無效果第二日又來<br />\n<br />\n或者持續到幾日後</blockquote><br />\nD藥同抑鬱症一樣都正常，因為醫生多數都係會用抗抑鬱藥嚟醫焦慮症，同埋要嚟醫焦慮症嘅劑量會高過醫抑鬱添<br />\n初頭開始食啲藥可能個人反而會緊張咗，呢個情況都係正常嘅，因為啲藥調節緊你腦入面嘅化學物質，會影響你情緒<br />\n但只要keep住食一段長時間，隻藥嘅治療效果就會慢慢表現到出嚟<br />\n個人應該可以放鬆啲同埋胃口都會好咗<br />\n<br />\n其實焦慮症同普通傷風感冒一樣都只係一種病，只要食藥睇醫生就一定會好，不過要畀啲時間<br />\n<br />\n一定要相信醫生同啲藥可以幫到你，焦慮症唔會陪你一世，因為你已經作出咗對付佢嘅行動，情況一定會改變"},{"pid":"8f49c142e9639029c890fd56fb5d9c6566fcd8a4","tid":92171,"uid":78473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T13:01:11.000Z","msg":"焦慮<br />\n強迫<br />\n潔癖<br />\n被迫害妄想<br />\n加少少完美主義<br />\n<br />\n日日都過得好辛苦"},{"pid":"909a00d7e5ded28dfd4e41d2baa2e0fb7f0dc395","tid":92171,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T13:05:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>焦慮<br />\n強迫<br />\n潔癖<br />\n被迫害妄想<br />\n加少少完美主義<br />\n<br />\n日日都過得好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n食咩藥"},{"pid":"20bebe11423c1a1006bc723427c3d80d060e0627","tid":92171,"uid":78473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T13:06:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>焦慮<br />\n強迫<br />\n潔癖<br />\n被迫害妄想<br />\n加少少完美主義<br />\n<br />\n日日都過得好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n食咩藥</blockquote><br />\n無食"},{"pid":"fc4363e9f500fcd7fd7adb632e4a1de54d5d7353","tid":92171,"uid":19073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T13:37:48.000Z","msg":"成日諗得太多 每樣野都諗如果咁做之後會點 到時要點處理點應付 諗多好多個下一步 咁呢個算唔算係焦慮症？ 同埋無論係個腦定全身都好似放鬆唔到"}]}